# BidVault Frontend Environment Variables (Example for Live Production Deployment)
# When deploying to Vercel / Netlify / Cloudflare Pages, add these in your Project Settings -> Environment Variables:

# 1. Backend API Base URL
# Replace with your Live Backend URL hosted on Render / Railway / AWS
VITE_API=https://bidvault-backend.onrender.com

# 2. Socket.io Realtime Server URL
# Usually identical to your VITE_API URL
VITE_SOCKET_URL=https://bidvault-backend.onrender.com
